# apps/backend/src/modules/knowledge/

## Responsibility
Handles knowledge sources, ingestion metadata, retrieval testing, categories, and indexing workflows.

## Design
Service + indexing/extraction pipeline for text, docs, audio, image, and URL sources. Retrieval tests can run against selected sources and emit metrics.

## Flow
Routes list/create/update/delete sources and categories, upload files, normalize content, and call retrievalTest for answer generation and chunk grounding.

## Integration
Depends on MediaService for uploads, AIService for retrieval/runtime, and Prisma-backed source/chunk/category storage.

